def save_latest_excel():
    url = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/classement"
    res = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(res.content, 'html.parser')
    
    tables = soup.find_all(class_ = "rankings__download")
    for table in tables:
        file_name = re.findall("/download-race-data/(vendeeglobe_\d+_\d+.xlsx)", str(table))[0]
    url_1 = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/download-race-data/"
    url_file = url_1 + file_name
    resp = requests.get(url_file)
    with open(file_name, 'wb') as outfile:
        outfile.write(resp.content)

def save_previous_excel():
    url = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/classement"
    res = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(res.content, 'html.parser')

    tables = soup.find_all(class_ = "boats-list__popup-specs-list")
    file_names = re.findall('\d+_\d+', str(tables))

    url_1 = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/download-race-data/"
    for file_name in file_names:
        url_file = url_1 + 'vendeeglobe_' + file_name + '.xlsx'
        file_name = 'vendeeglobe_' + file_name + '.xlsx'
        resp = requests.get(url_file)
        with open(file_name, 'wb') as outfile:
            outfile.write(resp.content)

def save_technical_specs():
    url = "https://www.vendeeglobe.org/fr/glossaire"
    res = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(res.content, 'html.parser')
    tables = soup.find_all(class_ = "boats-list__popup-specs-list")
    with open(path_project+'/'+'tech_spec.csv', 'wb') as outfile:
        outfile.write(str(tables).encode('utf-8'))        
    return str(tables)

def excel_format(file):       
    wb = xw.Book(file)
    xw.Range('B4:B5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('C4:C5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('D4:D5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('E4:G4').unmerge()
    hour = xw.Range('E5').value
    xw.Range('E4').value = hour
    latitude = xw.Range('F5').value
    xw.Range('F4').value = latitude
    longitude = xw.Range('G5').value
    xw.Range('G4').value = longitude
    xw.Range('H4:K4').unmerge()
    xw.Range('H4').value = 'heading_30'
    xw.Range('I4').value = 'speed_30'
    xw.Range('J4').value = 'VMG_30'
    xw.Range('K4').value = 'distance_30'
    xw.Range('L4:O4').unmerge()
    xw.Range('L4').value = 'heading_last'
    xw.Range('M4').value = 'speed_last'
    xw.Range('N4').value = 'VMG_last'
    xw.Range('O4').value = 'distance_last'
    xw.Range('P4:S4').unmerge()
    xw.Range('P4').value = 'heading_24'
    xw.Range('Q4').value = 'speed_24'
    xw.Range('R4').value = 'VMG_24'
    xw.Range('S4').value = 'distance_24'
    xw.Range('T4:T5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('U4:U5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('1:3').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('2:2').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('A:A').api.Delete()
    wb.save()
    wb.close()

def format_latest_file(file):
    wb = xw.Book(file)
    xw.Range('B4:B5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('C4:C5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('D4:D5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('E4:H5').unmerge()
    arrival_date = xw.Range('E4').value
    xw.Range('H4').value = arrival_date
    xw.Range('E:G').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('F4:I5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('E4:H5').unmerge()
    xw.Range('F:I').unmerge()
    xw.Range('G:I').api.Delete()
    gap_to_first = xw.Range('G5').value
    xw.Range('H4').value = gap_to_first
    xw.Range('G:G').api.Delete()
    gap_to_previous = xw.Range('H5').value
    xw.Range('I4').value = gap_to_previous
    xw.Range('H:H').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('I4').value = 'Speed over ortho'
    xw.Range('J4').value = 'Distance over ortho'
    xw.Range('K4').value = 'Percentage'
    xw.Range('L4').value = 'Speed over ground'
    xw.Range('M4').value = 'Distance over ground'
    xw.Range('1:3').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('2:2').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('A:A').api.Delete()
    xw.Range('35:38').api.Delete()
    wb.save()
    wb.close()

latitude_num = []
for i in range(len(df['latitude'])):
    lat = re.findall(r"(\d{1,3})°(\d{1,3}).(\d{1,3})'([A-Z]{1})", df['latitude'].iloc[i])
    #print(lat)
    if (lat[0][3] == 'S'): 
        latitude_num.append(-(np.round(int(lat[0][0])+int(lat[0][1])/60+int(lat[0][2])/3600, 4)))
    else: 
        latitude_num.append((np.round(int(lat[0][0])+int(lat[0][1])/60+int(lat[0][2])/3600, 4)))
